text: Børge Minerth (2 April 1920 - 19 March 1980) was a Danish gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:1980 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
